actions.comment:
Thanks for filing this. You're right that `CanvasSize` is exposed on every other platform view but missing from the Blazor components.

As a workaround, you can access the canvas size from within the `OnPaintSurface` callback via `e.Info.Size`:

```csharp
void OnPaintSurface(SKPaintSurfaceEventArgs e)
{
    var canvasSize = e.Info.Size;
    // use canvasSize for layout calculations
}
```

This doesn't help if you need the size outside of the paint callback, but it covers the most common use case. The fix itself would be a one-liner on each component: `public SKSize CanvasSize => canvasSize;`
